  "content_id": "b66b2fce-af35-43ba-8d72-67ff653ab114",
  "description": "Get advice and training if you are an employer and you want to retain and recruit employees who are also carers - telephone, email, website",
  "details": {
    "body": "\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>Advice and training for employers with employees who are carers.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Employers for Carers</strong> <br>\n<a href=\"http://www.employersforcarers.org\">www.employersforcarers.org</a><br>\n<a href=\"mailto:employers@carersuk.org\">employers@carersuk.org</a> <br>\nTelephone: 020 7378 4956  <br>\n<a href=\"/call-charges\">Find out about call charges</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<p>You can get advice about:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>identifying carers in the workplace</li>\n  <li>managing staff carer networks</li>\n  <li>directing staff to other sources of support outside the workplace</li>\n  <li>practical solutions to combining work and care</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>You can get training to help you with:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>employment law</li>\n  <li>carers rights</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/flexible-working\">flexible working</a></li>\n  <li>managing stress</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>Employers for Carers is a partner organisation of <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.carersuk.org/\">Carers UK.</a></p>\n</div>\n",
    "external_related_links": [
      {
        "title": "Carers UK",
        "url": "http://www.carersuk.org/"
      }
    ]
  },
